OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1780056672
OL,3,CMan stabbed at event in Carrickfergus
OL,5,FAn appeal for information has been
OL,6,Fmade after a man was stabbed at an
OL,7,Fevent in Carrickfergus.
OL,9,FPolice said the victim was stabbed in
OL,10,Fthe chest and also received injuries
OL,11,Fto his head in the incident in the
OL,12,FRodgers Quay area shortly after 7.30pm
OL,13,Fon Wednesday.
OL,15,FIt is understood to have happened
OL,16,Fduring a motorcycle event.
OL,18,FA police spokesperson said a male
OL,19,Fsuspect reportedly fled the scene on
OL,20,Fthe back of a motorbike following the
OL,21,Faltercation.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/5
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
