FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1780056672
OL,3,CMan stabbed at event in Carrickfergus
OL,5,F"He is described as being
OL,6,Fapproximately six feet in height, of
OL,7,Fmedium build, and aged in his 40s,"
OL,8,Fthey said.
OL,10,F"The victim was taken to hospital for
OL,11,Ftreatment for his injuries following
OL,12,Fthe incident. At this time, they are
OL,13,Fnot believed to be life threatening.
OL,15,F"There were a large number of people
OL,16,Fin the area at the time of the
OL,17,Fincident, and we would urge anyone who
OL,18,Fcan assist us with our enquiries, or
OL,19,Fwho has any information which could
OL,20,Fhelp, to get in touch.
OL,26,@mD@AOUoD@cO]rD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/5
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1780056672
OL,3,CMan stabbed at event in Carrickfergus
OL,5,F"Police are aware that this incident
OL,6,Foccurred at an event which takes place
OL,7,Fon a regular basis, and generally
OL,8,Fpasses off peacefully with no issues.
OL,10,F"The number to call is 101, quoting
OL,11,Freference number 1557 of 27/05/26."
OL,13,FAlliance MLA Stewart Dickson expressed
OL,14,Fshock at the incident.
OL,16,F"For the past number of weeks hundreds
OL,17,Fof bikers have been making the trip to
OL,18,FCarrickfergus for friendship and
OL,19,Fcamaraderie as the bike meet continued
OL,20,Fto grow in popularity," he said.
OL,26,@mD@AOUrD@AOUsD@cO]xD@AOU|D@WO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/5
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1780056672
OL,3,CMan stabbed at event in Carrickfergus
OL,5,F"I know a lot of hard work by the
OL,6,Forganisers went into making this event
OL,7,Fa welcoming space.
OL,9,F"Sadly, what occurred on Wednesday
OL,10,Fnight was not in keeping with the
OL,11,Foverall ethos of what the storming of
OL,12,Fthe castle bike meet was intended to
OL,13,Fbe.
OL,15,F"I am shocked at this stabbing,
OL,16,Fparticularly as it has resulted in
OL,17,Flife-altering injuries for the victim
OL,18,Fand we must pay tribute to all the
OL,19,Femergency services involved last night.
OL,26,@mD@AOUqD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/5
